(80, 1, '2018-01-24 07:56:18', '2018-01-24 07:56:18', '&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12\">\r\n<h1>Astra Timeline &amp; Roadmap</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"timeline\">\r\n<div class=\"center-line\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"year\">\r\n<div class=\"name\">2017</div>\r\n<div class=\"items cf\">\r\n<div class=\"item left\">\r\n<div class=\"date\">Q1</div>\r\n<div class=\"box\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title\">CONCEPTUALIZATION</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n\r\nInitial assessment of computing resources required by our scientists for data-driven research and the resources actually available to them. Investigated the causes behind decline in shared computing networks. Conceptualized Astra  The Social Supercomputer project.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item right\">\r\n<div class=\"date\">Q2</div>\r\n<div class=\"box\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title\">CUSTOMER VALIDATION</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n\r\nAstra project validation with research groups. Developed strategies for raising the value of Astra Tokens (STARs). Developed the Astra Whitepaper, technical roadmap, and business plan.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item left\">\r\n<div class=\"date\">Q3</div>\r\n<div class=\"box\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title\">COMMUNITY BUILDING</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n\r\nPresented Astra project at various Meetups in Silicon Valley to gather consumer feedback. Initiated the process for online Astra communities. Built engineering team and early project backers.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item right\">\r\n<div class=\"date\">Q4</div>\r\n<div class=\"box\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title\">Preparation for Token Sale</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n\r\nInvestigated regulatory landscape for fund-raising and compliant token sale in early 2018. Prepared the Marketing Plan and literature for raising awareness of the Astra Project around the world.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"year\">\r\n<div class=\"name\">2018</div>\r\n<div class=\"items cf\">\r\n<div class=\"item left\">\r\n<div class=\"date\">Q1</div>\r\n<div class=\"box\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title\">UNIFIED ASTRA APP</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n\r\nUnified Astra App: An intuitive interface to the numerous Sharing Networks, so that consumers dont have to download, install, and setup a confusing array of individual software programs.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item right\">\r\n<div class=\"date\">Q2</div>\r\n<div class=\"box\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title\">DECISION AUTOMATION</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n\r\nDecision Automation: Optimum selection of a Sharing Network that maximizes returns in Digital Currencies. Automatic selection of optimal options for each Sharing Network so that consumers dont have to learn about their intricacies.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item left\">\r\n<div class=\"date\">Q3</div>\r\n<div class=\"box\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title\">Astra Communities</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n\r\nAstra is transforming passive volunteer communities into vibrant economic communities where members have strong incentives to share computing resources and create valuable content and digital assets. Astra will also offer a suite of tools for building and nurturing action-oriented communities.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"item right\">\r\n<div class=\"date\">Q4</div>\r\n<div class=\"box\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title\">Community Incentive System</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n\r\nThe design and testing of an effective monetary policy that fully captures the present and future value of Global Networks and Communities that Astra is building. Community incentives in the form of Community Coins and Virtual Tradable Assets.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"year\">\r\n<div class=\"name\">2019</div>\r\n<div class=\"items cf\">\r\n<div class=\"item left\">\r\n<div class=\"date\">Q1</div>\r\n<div class=\"box\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title\">Application Launch System</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n\r\nAn intuitive platform to build and launch distributed computing projects on Astra Network. The scientists, researchers, and commercial organizations can create their applications in any environment and Astra will be able to launch them on any Sharing Network.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"gfts\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 text-right\">\r\n                                <a class=\"appsLand-btn appsLand-btn-gradient btn-inverse scrollLink\" href=\"#\"><span>Private Pre-distribution</span></a>\r\n<p class=\"text-center-tt\">From Oct 15th</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 text-left\">\r\n                                <a class=\"appsLand-btn appsLand-btn-gradient btn-inverse scrollLink\" href=\"#\"><span>Public Distribution</span></a>\r\n<p class=\"text-center-tt\">From Nov 15th</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n-->\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Roadmap', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-24 07:56:18', '2018-01-24 07:56:18', '', 9, 'https://demo-octalogo.com/astraa-wp/2018/01/24/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
